reviewText: This season was epic. Loved the Tori and Kayla as a couple. They're great together and balance each other out. Great drama!!! Can't wait to see the new series Lovers and Friends LA.
Bad dvd quality and hard to navigate the menu.
The biggest problem was the sound. It really disrupted your enjoyment of the series.
Loved the season as a whole....it didn't exactly wrap up every body's situation the way I hoped it would've but good nonetheless...wish there were more
You either hate it or love it .... Personally ive loved this show from the beginning. Plus Nicole Pina is GORGEOUS.
I love the season very interesting, however the episodes were rushed and the recording of the film could've been better. But overall I enjoyed the movie.
